Vettaiyan is an upcoming Indian Tamil-language action drama film directed by T. J. Gnanavel and produced by Subaskaran's Lyca Productions. The film stars Rajinikanth in the titular role, alongside Amitabh Bachchan, Fahadh Faasil, Rana Daggubati, Manju Warrier, Ritika Singh, Dushara Vijayan and Abhirami. It is the thirtieth production for the studio and marks the Tamil debut of Bachchan.

snippet.title: क्या Iyer और Jetha खा पाएँगे इतना बड़ा Sada Dosa? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony SAB Channel:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

The men from the Gokuldham society are shocked that the ladies did not pick up the call. The ladies file a complaint at the police station about the bike. The society members are tensed that the ladies did not receive a call even after consistently trying it. Bhide and the society members are shocked after learning that Madhavi has filed a complaint about a bike stolen from the market before. Inspector Chalu Pande assures Bhide that the search team is consistently tracing the location of his bike and will find it soon. 

Show Name: Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast: Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt 
Produced By: Asit Kumar Modi 

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #sab #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble for all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son, he calls his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal. 

Click here to watch more episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7a-p97oXBuuoyLMAq7Ktx_h
 
क्या Iyer और Jetha खा पाएँगे इतना बड़ा Sada Dosa? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

snippet.title: Durga Ji Ki Aarti - Jai Ambe Gauri Full with Lyrics | Mata Ki Aarti | माता जी की आरती | दुर्गा आरती
snippet.description:
Durga Ji Ki Aarti - Jai Ambe Gauri Full with Lyrics | Mata Ki Aarti | माता जी की आरती | दुर्गा आरती

Tips Bhakti Prem Presents Navratri Most Popular "Jai Ambe Gauri Aarti" With Lyrics Sung By Alka Yagnik. watch on @tipsbhaktiprem 

#durgamantra #navdurgamantra #navratrimantra #navratri2024 

To receive regular updates on devotional songs subscribe to us on the following link: https://www.youtube.com/BhaktiPrem

Song Credits :
Singer : Alka Yagnik
Lyrics : Traditional
Music Composer : Sayed Ali

Lyrics :
Jai Ambe Gauri, Maiya Jai Durga Gauri
जय अम्बे गौरी, मैया जय दुर्गा गौरी
Tumko Nishdin Dhyavat, 
तुमको निशदिन ध्यावत 
Tumko Nishdin Dhyavat, 
तुमको निशदिन ध्यावत
Brahma Hari Shivji
ब्रह्मा हरि शिवजी 
Om Jai Ambe Gauri
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी

Maang Sindoor Virajat, Tiko Jagmag Ko
मांग सिंदूर विराजत, टीको जगमग को
Maiya Tiko Jagmag Ko
मैया टीको जगमग को
Ujjwal Se Do Naina, Chandra Wadan Neeko
उज्ज्वल से दो नैना, चंद्र वदन नीको
Om Jai Ambe Gauri
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी

Kanak Samaan Kalevar, Raktambar Raaje
कनक समान कलेवर, रक्ताम्बर राजै
Maiya Raktambar Raaje
मैया रक्ताम्बर राजै
Rakta pushp Gal Mala, Kanthan Par Saaje
रक्त पुष्प गल माला, कंठन पर साजै
Om Jai Ambe Gauri
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी


Ke Hari Vahan Rajat, Khadag Khappar Dhaari
के हरि वाहन राजत, खड्ग खप्पर धारी
Maiya Khadag Khappar Dhaari
मैया खड्ग खप्पर धारी
Sur-Nar-Munijan Sevat, Tinke Dukh Haari
सुर-नर-मुनिजन सेवत, तिनके दुखहारी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी

Kanan Kundal Shobhit, Naasagre Moti
कानन कुण्डल शोभित, नासाग्रे मोती
Maiya Naasagre Moti
मैया नासाग्रे मोती
Kotik Chandra Divakar, Sam Rajat Jyoti
कोटिक चंद्र दिवाकर, सम राजत ज्योती
Om Jai Ambe Gauri
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी

Shumbh-Nishumbh Vidare, Mahishasur Ghaati
शुंभ-निशुंभ बिदारे, महिषासुर घाती
Maiya Mahishasur Ghaati
मैया महिषासुर घाती
Dhumra  Vilochan Naina, Nis Din Madamati
धूम्र विलोचन नैना, निस दिन मदमाती
Om Jai Ambe Gauri
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी

Chand-Mund Sanhare, Shonit Beej Hare
चण्ड-मुण्ड संहारे, शोणित बीज हरे
Maiya Shonit Beej Hare
मैया शोणित बीज हरे
Madhu-Kaitabh Dou Maare, Sur Bhayhin Kare
मधु-कैटभ दोउ मारे, सुर भयहीन करे
Om Jai Ambe Gauri
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी

Bramhani, Rudrani,Tum Kamala Rani
ब्रह्माणी, रूद्राणी, तुम कमला रानी
Maiya Tum Kamla Rani
मैया तुम कमला रानी
Agam Nigam Ne Bakhani, Tum Shiv Patrani
आगम निगम ने बखानी, तुम शिव पटरानी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी

Chausath Yogini Gavat, Nritya Karat Bhairo
चौंसठ योगिनी गावत, नृत्य करत भैरों
Maiya Nritya Karat Bhairo
मैया नृत्य करत भैरों
Bajat Taal Mridanga, Aru Baajat Damaru
बाजत ताल मृदंगा, अरू बाजत डमरू
Om Jai Ambe Gauri
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी

Tum Hi Jag Ki Maata, Tum Hi Ho Bharta
तुम ही जग की माता, तुम ही हो भरता
Maiya Tum Hi Ho Bharta
मैया तुम ही हो भरता
Bhaktan Ki Dukh Harta, Sukh Sampati Karta
भक्तन की दुख हरता, सुख संपति करता
Om Jai Ambe Gauri
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी

Bhuja Char Ati Shobhit, Var Mudra Dhari xx
भुजा चार अति शोभित, वर-मुद्रा धारी
Maiya Var Mudra Dhari
मैया वर-मुद्रा धारी
Mann Vaanchhit Phal Paavat, Sevat Nar Naari
मनवांछित फल पावत, सेवत नर नारी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी

Kanchan Thaal Virajat, Agar Kapoor Baati
कंचन थाल विराजत, अगर कपूर बाती
Maiya Agar Kapoor Baati
मैया अगर कपूर बाती
Shrimaalketu Mein Rajat, Koti Ratan Jyoti
श्रीमालकेतु में राजत, कोटि रतन ज्योती
Om Jai Ambe Gauri
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी

Shree Ambeji Ki Aarti, Jo Koi Nar Gaave
श्री अंबेजी की आरति, जो कोइ नर गावे
Maiya Jo Koi Nar Gaave
मैया जो कोइ नर गावे
Kehat Shivanand Swami, Sukh-Sampatti Paave
कहत शिवानंद स्वामी, सुख-संपति पावे
Om Jai Ambe Gauri
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी

Jai Ambe Gauri, Maiya Jai Durga Gauri
जय अम्बे गौरी, मैया जय दुर्गा गौरी
Tumko Nishdin Dhyavat, 
तुमको निशदिन ध्यावत 
Tumko Nishdin Dhyavat, 
तुमको निशदिन ध्यावत
Brahma Hari Shivji
ब्रह्मा हरि शिवजी 
Om Jai Ambe Gauri
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी

Welcome to my Youtube Channel,
I'm Jonathan Amaral, you might know me as Jonathan Gaming.
I started my professional Esports Career competing in Pubg Mobile Championships (Now BGMI),
Since the start of my career, I have been consistent with my gameplay and always been working hard to achieve my goals via winning Domestic/Global Championships. 
"The only player you should try to be better than is the player you were yesterday."
I Stream BGMI regularly, I also enjoy playing Valorant and other fun games once in a while!

snippet.title: "என் தம்பி சாந்தனுவும் நானும் Normal-ஆ பேசிக்க மாட்டோம்; அதனாலதான்..." 😳 - Actress Saranya Breaking
snippet.description:
#sharanyabhagyaraj #saranyabhagyaraj #vijay #prithviraj #bhagyaraj #shanthanu #shanthanubhagyaraj #parijathammovie #tamilcinema #actress 

"என் தம்பி சாந்தனுவும் நானும் Normal-ஆ பேசிக்க மாட்டோம்; அதனாலதான்..." 😳 - Actress Saranya Breaking


நடிகர் மற்றும் இயக்குநர் பாக்யராஜின் மூத்த மகள் சரண்யா பாக்யராஜ். தன் அப்பா பாக்யராஜ் இயக்கிய 'பாரிஜாதம்' திரைப்படத்தில் நாயகியாக நடித்த சரண்யா, அதன்பிறகு, எங்கே போனார், என்ன செய்கிறார் என தெரியாமல் இருந்தது. 18 ஆண்டுகளாக சினிமாவில் நடிக்காமல் இருக்கும் சரண்யா, முதல்முறையாக தன் பர்சனல் விஷயங்கள் குறித்து மனம் திறந்து பேசியிருக்கிறார், இந்தப் பேட்டியில்.

------------------------------------------------

Cameraman : Sathish Kumar

------------------------------------------------

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kaffara Episode 80 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 8th October 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

snippet.description:
Get ready for an explosive experience with 'Pistol' by Gagan Kokri featuring Gurlez Akhtar! 🎵🔥 White Hill Music brings you a captivating new Punjabi song video for 2024 with powerful vocals by Gagan Kokri, lyrics by RHYME Gill, and music by MRXCI. 'Pistol' is a high-energy track that combines raw emotion with electrifying beats, making it the next viral hit! 🌟 Subscribe for more new Punjabi songs 2024 and share your feelings in the comments!

🎧 YouTube Music: https://music.youtube.com/watch?v=Zmy671HYZ34&si=-DnzuX8EDX1G5Knr
🎶 JioSaavn:  https://www.jiosaavn.com/album/pistol/2WktkFYLIXQ_
🎧 Gaana: https://gaana.com/song/pistol-155
🎵 Wynk:  


👁️‍🗨️ Lyrics :

Haye ve jatta pistol waleya
Haye ve jatta pistol waleya
Haye ve jatta pistol waleya
Haye ve jatta pistol waleya

Je kardi donaliya ni fail teri akh ni
Main maju ke blood line jinni rakha agg ni
Gabhru da tod ni rakane is jag te
Oh bheda naal bhajde ni ghode change lagde
Sun ley ni jatt pistola aale aa
Baliye ni jatt pistola aale aa
Sun ley ni jatt pistola aale aa
Sun ley ni jatt pistola aale aa

Haan ankh aa karachi di
Te nakhra milaan da
Affiness car jeha husan rakan da
Buliya te narmi da banda mahool ve
Main velliyan da hatha cho chudhate pistol ve
Oh garm subah di jatti soft ji tone jatta
Oh tiffni di ring meri ankh da clone jatta

Oh jithe kam gunna de khadak vi ni kadd de
Othe kam kadh dindi rehke kudi mon jatta
Oh killa sultan da kharid leya yaar ne 
Shikariya ne karte shikar mutiyaar ne 
Naam sun gabhru da kamb jande shehar ne
Goli toh jawani jatta bangi aa fire ve
Sun ley ve jatta pistol waleya
Sun ley ve jatta pistol waleya

Khada jatt asle varga naal 
Ni combination dekh kamaal 
Je golii jach di ae jatta gun na 
Tere naal khadi jachugi naar
Tere te mar gayi ve 
Ruffle de vargi ve 
Load akh asle nu
Fail si kar gi ve
Oh kokri aa pind munda 
Sandhu aa de lane da 
Kabadi vich naam jive chilu haryane da 
Oh gutt de potek lagi kuff thode fold aa
Jo duniya chilonde call ona di vi hold aa
Oh goli aala masla jawaniya nu ro lda
Ve role wala zindagi ch hunda pistol da
Load kar rakhya hove taan gal hor aa
Oda tun hatha vi kisi nu ki aa golda
Oh rhyme gill karda belong jede pind ton 
Oh churdh chak wale teri pur de lehaj ne
Pehla  jattan chakeya sawad nu tu asla
Aaj chadh sakda ni eho je halaat ne
Sun ley taahi te pistol rakhe aa
Jattiye taahi te pistol rakhe aa
Sun ley taahi te pistol rakhe aa

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kaffara Episode 79 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 7th October 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

snippet.title: Matka Teaser | Varun Tej | Karuna Kumar | Meenakshi Chowdary | Nora Fatehi | GV Prakash Kumar
snippet.description:
Get ready for a high-octane experience with the action-packed teaser of  #Matka! Featuring Varun Tej, Meenakshi Chowdary, and Nora Fatehi, with a powerful soundtrack by GV Prakash Kumar, directed by Karuna Kumar. A thrilling treat awaits!

Stay updated with the latest videos, Subscribe on the link - http://bit.ly/adityamusic
Click here to share on Facebook- https://bit.ly/3v3iHeg  

#MATKA is an upcoming Periodical Film starring Mega Prince Varun tej in the Lead Role, Written and Directed by Karuna Kumar. It also co stars Meenakshi Chowdary, Nora Fatehi, Naveen Chandra and others. Music by GV Prakash Kumar, Cinematography by A Kishor Kumar and Proudly Produced on a massive scale by Dr. Vijender Reddy Teegala and Rajani Talluri under Vyra Entertainments in Association with SRT Entertainments

The story which takes place between 1958-1982 is based on a real incident that shook the entire nation and the story is set in the backdrop of Vizag. The story spans 24 years. 

Cast: #VarunTej, #MeenakshiChowdary, #NoraFatehi, Naveen Chandra, Kannada Kishore, Ajay Ghosh, Mime Gopi, Roopalakshmi, Vijayrama Raju, Jagadeesh, Raj Thirandas.

Jaan Nisar Episode 59 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Danish Taimoor - Hiba Bukhari - Haroon Shahid - 5th October 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment’s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi’s love?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Mohsin Mirza
Writer: Rehana Aftab

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:

Finally, We eat this Tutti Frutti with Ice Cream! Yummy!

snippet.title: Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Ganesh Master || Velli Vastha || Climax Episode || MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu Ganesh Master Velli Vastha Climax Episode MCM
Filmymoji Kannada :- https://www.youtube.com/@FilmymojiKannada-y3x
"In this Filmymoji  Middle Class Madhu episode, Madhu and his friends are sitting in the pandiri (a gathering spot) chatting when they receive a message from the principal's office. The principal orders them to clean up the premises immediately, leaving everyone disappointed. They return to the pandiri and discuss their bond with Ganesh Master, telling him that if he needs anything, the Nattugunta gang is always there for him. Later, a boy who can't afford the fees decides to commit suicide by going to the top floor, but Madhu and friends rescue him and set out to clean up the premises. What happens next is what makes this episode a delightful mix of comedy and emotion. Watch this episode to enjoy."

snippet.title: Hospital में CID ने रंगे हाथों पकड़ा Heart Scam | CID | Full Episode 820 | 4 Oct 2024
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Dr. Salunke's examination of the deceased's body reveals something unusual. Despite the appearance of a heart attack, Dr. Salunke detects signs of foul play that indicate the death was not natural. Further investigation uncovers evidence suggesting that the victim was poisoned, leading CID to conclude that the apparent heart attack was, in fact, a murder orchestrated by someone with malicious intent.


Show name: CID
Starcast: Shivaji Satam, Dayanand Shetty, Aditya Srivastav
Produced by: B.P. Singh
Episode Number: 820

#CID #सीआईडी #sonypal #NewCID #LatestCID #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries#CID #सीआईडी #cid2024 

About CID: 
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Click here to watch the full episodes of CID:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1tkfTmeItT5VvhD8JbNitp

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS |  Real Madrid 2-0 Villarreal | LaLiga 2024/25
snippet.description:
Real Madrid will head into the international break having taken all three points against third-placed Villarreal at the Bernabéu. Ancelotti's men secured the win with two superb strikes from outside the box. The first was by Valverde after a well-rehearsed move from a corner-kick. On the quarter-hour mark, Modrić took a short corner, Bellingham tricked the defence by letting the ball run past him and Valverde did the rest. The Uruguayan hit a fierce first-time strike from outside the area which flew past Diego Conde with the help of a deflection off Baena. In the second half and Vini Jr. scored with a spectacular right-footed finish. In the 70th minute, the Brazilian picked up the ball on the edge of the box and swerved a strike into the top corner giving Diego Conde no chance.Madrid extended their unbeaten run in LaLiga to 41 games (30 wins and 11 draws). The downside came in stoppage time when Carvajal was stretchered off in considerable pain and received a standing ovation from the home fans.
#RealMadridVillarreal | #LaLigaHighlights

es.title: RESUMEN | Real Madrid 2-0 Villarreal | LaLiga 2024/25
es.description:
El Real Madrid se marchó al parón por los compromisos de selecciones sumando los tres puntos frente al Villarreal. Los de Ancelotti lograron el triunfo con dos grande tantos desde fuera del área: primero marcó Valverde en una jugada ensayada. Aún no se había cumplido el cuarto de hora cuando Modrić sacó el córner, Bellingham engañó a la defensa dejando pasar el balón y Valverde hizo el resto. Recibió fuera del área, disparó con enorme potencia y superó a Diego Conde previo impacto del esférico en el cuerpo de Baena. En la segunda parte lo hizo Vini Jr. con un derechazo espectacular. 
El brasileño recibió escorado dentro del área en el 70’ e intentó sorprender con un remate al primer palo. El balón terminó en el lateral de la red. Tres minutos después llegó su golazo. El Madrid encadena 41 partidos invictos en la Liga (30 victorias y 11 empates). La nota negativa llegó ya en el añadido cuando Carvajal se tuvo que retirar en camilla y ovacionado con ostensibles gestos de dolor.

snippet.title: Navratri 2024 | Aigiri Nandini With Meaning in Hindi | Mahishasur Mardini Stotra | Madhubanti Bagchi
snippet.description:
Tilak Originals Presents, Aigiri Nandini, a beautiful version of the Mahishasura Mardini Stotram With Hindi Translataion. This captivating Stotram is Sung by Madhubanti Bagchi and brought to life with amazing music by Siddharth Amit Bhavsar, this Stotram is all about the fierce and loving spirit of Maa Durga.

As you listen, you'll not only enjoy the powerful melodies but also find Hindi translations that make the meaning come alive! It’s a perfect way to connect with the strength and grace of the Goddess Durga as she fights against darkness and evil.

With Navratri upon us, we want to wish you all a joyful celebration! May Maa Durga bless you with happiness, strength, and positivity during these special days.

Let’s celebrate together! Happy Navratri! Jai Maa Durga! ✨
